@node history "History"

	4.1 - Switched to using MiniView as AmigaGuide viewer. As a result
	      all nodes now open in the same guide window again. I missed that :-)

	      Bugfix: Cancelling string requester no longer displays "result"
	      node.

	      Updated rmh.xref to match the guide for rmh.library v21.4.

 	      Code cleanup.

	      Note: The Leaveroom option doesn't seem to be working when using
		WinUAE.

	4.0a - Reupload with ArexxGuide xref file included.

	4.0 - Major rewrite. Sort of a 'back to basics' release :-) 

	      No longer uses any external Amigaguide viewers. Node is displayed
	      using shownode(). 

	      No more messing with ArexxGuide env vars.

	      Added support for alias'ed function names (Eg: rmh_readargs() ->
	      readargs().

	      Added xrefdir for easy organization of xref files.

	      Added support for CED leaveroom command.

	      Added rmh.library xref file.
                 
	      Rewrote/reorganized parts of the guide file.

	      Reworked xref files.

@endnode
